The paper deals with information theory and the quantification of information, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.ITP (Information Theory and Probability). The paper also discusses the concept of synergy, which is often studied in the context of machine learning and data analysis, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. The use of random variables and the Gacs-Korner common random variable suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
